sections.History:
===Background===
Lordsport was burned to the ground during the [[Greyjoy Rebellion]] as a prelude to the [[Siege of Pyke]] castle, but was rebuilt in intervening years.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Greyjoy Rebellion (Histories &amp; Lore)]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 2]]===
[[Theon Greyjoy]] arrives to Lordsport aboard the ''[[Myraham]]'', sent by [[Robb Stark]] as an envoy to discuss an alliance with [[Balon Greyjoy]].&lt;ref name=&quot;S2E02&quot;/&gt;

After choosing to side with his father in his conquest of [[the North]], Theon returns to Lordsport to meet the crew of the ''[[Sea Bitch]]'' and set sail.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
